203
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:21,260
Bet you didn't know that.

204
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:22,580
Actually I'm the hidden An San.

205
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:24,620
Anshan?

206
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:25,220
(Anshan?)

207
00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:27,380
Anshan? More like Tieling!

208
00:05:28,580 --> 00:05:29,940
You're from Anshan.

209
00:05:29,940 --> 00:05:30,900
Your name's Amino Acid.

210
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:31,620
(Amino Acid)

211
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:33,580
Amino Acid.

212
00:05:35,460 --> 00:05:36,860
